des:
Disclaimer: This skill calls an AI-Generated Parody of Trump!

Speak to Virtual Trump through your Alexa device. 

Trump will interact with you (with your name or any name you give), answer your questions and much more. Ask things like tell me a joke, thoughts on China, read Twitter, tell you facts, how are you, the border wall, Mexico and more!

***PREMIUM***
